name: Own The Sound - Beachcrimes - Own The Mixtape

metadata.description:
Own The Sound is excited to announce our first curated Music NFTs drop - ‘Beachcrimes - Own The Mixtape’. This vibrant mixtape showcases some of the best music and talent web3 has to offer.

The tracklist for this mixtape was crowdsourced, and Beachcrimes mixed it into a unique and eclectic listening experience:

Beachcrimes - NVM (0:00)
Vaarwell - Sellout (0:16)
Pauline Herr & LNRZ - Hold Me (0:18)
Edwin Honoret - How'd I Lose You (0:31)
Madalen Duke & Kevin George - Can't Stop (0:33)
Lincoln Jesser - Can't Help But To Think About You (0:40)
Lyrah & Reo Cragun - Head Above (0:47)
RŌHKI - Stars Won't Align (0:49)
Annika Rose - Lost (1:05)
Charlie Crown & Sara Phillips - Hurts (1:20)
Sammy Arriaga - METAGIRL (Remix) Feat. Nessy The Rilla (1:34)
